%20the%20discord%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gesture%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20reciprocated%20by%20TMC.%20Party%20supremo%20Banerjee%20made%20a%20scathing%20attack%20against%20her%20INDIA%20bloc%20partner%20and%20compared%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmere%20photo%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmigratory%20birds%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suggested%20the%20Congress%20fight%20on%20300%20seats%20but%20they%20refused.%20Now%2C%20they%20have%20come%20to%20the%20state%20to%20divide%20the%20Muslim%20voters.%20I%20doubt%20they%20would%20win%2040%20seats%20even%20if%20they%20contest%20300%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20was%20leading%20her%20own%20sit-in%20protest%20at%20Kolkata%20to%20demand%20the%20clearance%20of%20the%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20dues%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcpim-rahul-gandhi-bjny-bengal-mamata-banerjee%5C%22%3EIn%20Congress%20and%20CPI(M)%E2%80%99s%20Joint%20Nyay%20Yatra%20Show%20in%20Bengal%2C%20a%20Missive%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20also%20dared%20the%20Congress%20to%20try%20and%20topple%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20at%20its%20own%20backyard%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20wins%20in%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04124430%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-9.24.40-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22http