tion%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20The%20police%20also%20imposed%20several%20conditions%20including%20restricting%20Gandhi%20from%20greeting%20crowds%20directly%20and%20confining%20the%20Yatra%20to%20a%20five-vehicle%20convoy.%20According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20a%20few%20parents%20of%20students%20appearing%20for%20the%20board%20examinations%20had%20made%20complaints%20against%20Gandhi%20for%20causing%20inconvenience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20ambulance%20in%20the%20convoy%20collided%20with%20a%20vehicle%20carrying%20senior%20police%20officers%20near%20Jharkhand%20border.%20While%20neither%20Gandhi%20nor%20the%20police%20officers%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%2C%20the%20Birbhum%20police%20arrested%20two%20drivers%20and%20seized%20three%20vehicles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Yatra%20entered%20Jharkhand%20in%20the%20evening.%20It%20will%20pass%20through%2013%20districts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707031244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04124442%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-9.24.21-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-bengal-police%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20march%20left%20the%20state%20amidst%20much%20resistance%20from%20Bengal%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-bengal-police%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GST%20authorities%3A%20Penalty%20for%20Tobacco%20cos%20not%20registering%20packing%20machines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707031186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-12%2F16%2Ffull%