.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04105808%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20art%20of%20persistence%20is%20to%20be%20dead.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20A.%20N.%20Whitehead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20vermillion%2C%20saffron%20and%20celebrity%20crowds%20that%20can%20be%20bought%20cannot%20wash%20away%20the%20stench%20of%20crime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vilest%20organised%20criminal%20act%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20since%201947%20was%20committed%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20when%20the%2016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20Babri%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20the%20organisational%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20led%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20representing%20upper%20caste%20supremacism.%20Justice%20Liberhan%20in%20his%20report%20noted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2F20130103064212%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2FBabri-Masjid-demolition-neither-spontaneous-nor-unplanned-Liberhan%2FArticle1-479698.aspx%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20it%20stands%20established%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20the%20events%20of%20the%20day%20were%20neither%20spontaneous%20nor%20unplanned%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20inner%20core%20of%20the%20Parivar%2C%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20RSS%20(Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh)%2C%20VHP%20(Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20the%20BJP%20bear%20primary%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%20for%20this%20crime%20against%20the%20people%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20The%20date%20December%206%2C%201992%20marks%20our%20wasteful%20entrance%20to%20ruin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20we%20learn%20to%20read%20the%20auguries%20of%20this%20ruin%20and%20the%20celebration%20of%20its%20incomplete%20scaffolding%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20hoax%20of%20a%20political%20theatre%20%E2%80%93%20far%20worse%2C%20its%20obscene%20re-presentation%20in%20television%20studios%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20are%20expected%20to%20act%20like%20a%20(presentable)%20version%20of%20the%20BJP.%20This%20demand%20made%20of%20the%20opposition%20is%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20their%20very%20disappearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStages%20of%20demolition%20and%20the%20scaffolding%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conditions%20under%20which%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20demolition%20program%20was%20initiated%20was%20of%20increased%20contestation%20by%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20who%20are%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India.%20The%20looming%20of%20an%20anti-caste%20insurgency%20across%20India%20coincided%20with%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20completed%20Mandal%20commission%20report%20on%20December%2031%2C%201980.%20Both%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%2C%20later%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20kept%20the%20report%20in%20abeyance.%20It%20is%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20anti-caste%20movement%20and%20the%20explosive%20sequences%20of%20pogroms%20India%20witnessed%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20primarily%20against%20Muslims%20but%20also%20Christians%20and%20Sikhs%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20in%20order%20to%20make%20new%20choices%20about%20saving%20the%20Republic%20and%20its%20egalitarian%20promises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20significant%20events%20preceding%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Findia-at-75-epochal-moments-1986-babri-masjid-unlocked%2Farticle65730758.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20opening%20of%20its%20gates%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20in%201986.%20He%20had%20won%20the%20national%20elections%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fmodi-in-rajiv-gandhis-mirror%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20campaign%20of%20religious%20polarisation%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-terrorism%E2%80%9D%20hysteria%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20decades%20later%20to%20be%20matched%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%201987%20riots%20in%20Meerut%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20Muslims%2C%20where%20the%20Provincial%20Armed%20Constabulary%20(PAC)%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eparticipated.%20According%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpudr.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2019-02%2Fforgotten_massacre.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPUDR%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20riots%20which%20the%20PAC%20was%20supposedly%20called%20to%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%9Cceased%20to%20be%20riots%20and%20became%20PAC%20violence%20against%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20where%20the%20%E2%80%9CPAC%20indulged%20in%20large-scale%20arson%2C%20looting%20and%20burning%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20the%20pre-Babri%20demolition%20%E2%80%98riots%E2%80%99%20were%20locally%20preceded%20by%20lower%20caste%20assertions%20or%20caste%20contestations%2C%20among%20both%20%E2%80%98Hindus%E2%80%99%20and%20Muslims.%20The%20riots%20in%20October%201988%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Khatauli%2C%20and%20Aligarh%20in%20UP%20were%20conditioned%20by%20caste%20and%20religious%20contestations%20within%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Asghar%20Ali%20Engineer%20and%20K.%20S.%20Durani%20reported%20that%20upper%20and%20middle%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F4394214%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eurban%20petty%20bourgeois%20class%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20recently%20become%20prosperous%20sought%20political%20positions%20within%20the%20Congress%20party.%20While%20oppressing%20and%20exploiting%20the%20lower%20caste%20people%20they%20attempted%20to%20create%20%E2%80%9CHindu%E2%80%9D%20unity%20to%20dethrone%20an%20upper%20caste%20Muslim%20landlord%20in%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Upper%20caste%20Muslims%20were%20also%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20lower%20caste%20assertion%2C%20resulting%20in%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Ashraf-Ajlaf%20dichotomy%20among%20Muslims%20getting%20blurred%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque%2C%20where%20several%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20dignitaries%20of%20today%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fpm-ayodhya-flashback%2Farticleshow%2F107040898.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EM.%20M.%20Joshi%2C%20L.%20K.%20Advani%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cspan%3Ewere%20either%20present%20or%20had%20laid%20the%20ground%20work%2C%20pogroms%20against%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20euphemistically%20called%20%E2%80%98riots%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20spread%20throughout%20India%2C%20killing%20an%20estimated%202%2C000%20people.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriminals%20were%20never%20punished%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20very%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20nor%20for%20the%20mass%20murder%20of%20Muslims%20that%20preceded%20and%20followed%20the%20event.%20Instead%2C%20many%20were%20awarded%20cabinet%20ranks%20and%20other%20state%20honours%20in%20successive%20governments%2C%20including%20in%20the%20present%20one.%20Finally%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20legitimised%20and%20completed%20the%20processual%20conversion%20of%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20into%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20Rama%20temple%20as%20the%20achieved%20site%20and%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%E2%80%9D%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fayodhyas-ram-temple-a-stage-for-the-visible-display-of-bjps-extremely-backward-class-politics%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20Ram%20Temple%3A%20A%20Stage%20for%20the%20Visible%20Display%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20instruments%20of%20darkness%E2%80%9D%20often%20do%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-upper-castes-invented-hindu-majority%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20newspaper%20truthfully%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20movement%20at%20the%20time%3A%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20aura%20of%20Ram%2C%20the%20demon%20of%20Reservation%20ran%20away%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0That%20is%2C%20just%20as%20the%20recent%20celebrations%20were%20a%20scaffolding%20erected%20over%20a%20major%20crime%2C%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20unity%20is%20a%20scaffolding%20over%20caste%20oppression%20and%20lower%20caste%20assertions.%20The%20scaffolding%20is%20now%20a%20national%20project%3A%20as%20walls%20of%20tin%20erected%20around%20the%20poor%20when%20foreign%20dignitaries%20visit%3B%20as%20grand%20speeches%20around%20illegitimate%20court%20orders%3B%20and%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%9D%20around%20the%20ruins%20of%20all%20constitutional%20institutions%20including%20the%20Election%20Commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F27153406%2Fbabri_masjid-11302_2486082a-e1563521469520.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992.%20Photo%3A%20Sanjay%20Sharma%2FINDIAPIX%20NETWORK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20real%20lines%20of%20demarcation%20in%20politics%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-upper-castes-invented-hindu-majority%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereal%20contestation%20and%20the%20primary%20line%20of%20demarcation%20in%20Indian%20politics%20since%20the%2019th%20century%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20between%20the%20upper%20caste%20architects%20of%20Hindu%20identity%20and%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20who%20sought%20equal%20rights%20and%20proportional%20representation%20under%20modern%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20conditions.%20The%20Congress%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20and%20other%20smaller%20parties%20either%20emerged%20%E2%80%93%20or%20were%20impelled%20in%20their%20histories%20%E2%80%93%20as%20upper%20caste%20responses%20to%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20assertions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20events%20of%20contestation%2C%20barely%20discussed%2C%20determined%20regional%20and%20national%20politics%E2%80%94the%201948%20anti-Brahmin%20riots%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%201970%20Bhojpur%20insurgency%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%201968%20Kilvenmani%20massacre%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%201981%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2FGujarat-has-history-of-atrocities-and-discrimination-against-Dalits%2Farticle60527714.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E1985%20anti-reservation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20caste%20wars%20in%20Gujarat%20which%20explains%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fwebsite%2Fstory%2Fhistory-of-communal-violence-in-gujarat%2F217988%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhy%20this%20state%20is%20the%20capital%20of%20upper%20caste%20supremacism%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scaffolding%20inaugurated%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%20shows%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20political%20need%20for%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20to%20be%20given%20visibility%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20nominally%20and%20pejoratively%20%E2%80%93%20in%20public%20space.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fayodhyas-ram-temple-a-stage-for-the-visible-display-of-bjps-extremely-backward-class-politics%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERadhika%20Bordia%20reported%20from%20the%20temple%20site%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20main%20temple%20is%20dedicated%20to%20a%20Kshatriya%20King%2C%20there%20is%20a%20role%20for%20a%20supporting%20cast%2C%20such%20as%20the%20ancillary%20temple%20for%20Nishad%20Raj%20Guha%2C%20the%20king%20of%20the%20boatmen%2C%20who%20befriended%20Ram%20during%20his%20exile.%20%E2%80%A6This%20vision%20of%20Hinduism%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20challenge%20the%20Varna%20system%2C%20where%20the%20Shudra%20OBC%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Tribals%20are%20meant%20to%20play%20a%20supporting%20role%20to%20%E2%80%98upper%20caste%E2%80%99%20heroes.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20provide%20space%20and%20recognition%20to%20several%20communities%20that%2C%20until%20that%20point%2C%20had%20received%20little%20political%20acknowledgment%20in%20independent%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBordia%20points%20to%20the%20silence%20in%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F90-of-leadership-positions-in-indian-media-occupied-by-upper-caste-groups-report%2Farticle66010136.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E90%25%20of%20leadership%20positions%20in%20Indian%20media%20occupied%20by%20upper%20caste%20groups%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20about%20the%20process%20of%20Hinduisation%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20people.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20January%2022%20event%2C%20among%20the%20endless%20rituals%20and%20ceremonies%20being%20tracked%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20the%20series%20of%20events%20held%20by%20caste%20groups%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20most%20backward%20castes%20have%20largely%20been%20overlooked%E2%80%9D.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20autonomous%20Dalit-Bahujan%20political%20assemblies%20and%20organisation%20are%20criminalised%20by%20nearly%20all%20political%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20through%20the%20charges%20of%20terrorism%2C%20national%20security%2C%20%E2%80%98urban%20Naxalism%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20the%20process%20of%20the%20pejoration%20and%20absorption%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%2C%20often%20as%20%E2%80%98foot%20soldiers%E2%80%99%2C%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98the%20Hindu%E2%80%99%20order%20of%20oppression%20is%20quietly%20permitted%20by%20the%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%2C%20we%20come%20to%20the%20secondary%20line%20of%20demarcation%20in%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20Brahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20Brahminism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOn%20the%20bourgeois%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20terms%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20came%20to%20prominence%20through%20Marxist%20discourse%2C%20although%20various%20versions%20of%20these%20terms%20and%20analogous%20social%20conditions%20can%20be%20found%20earlier%2C%20including%20the%20derivation%20of%20the%20Marxist%20term%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eproletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20for%20those%20without%20property%20who%20survive%20through%20wage%20labour%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20Roman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20proletarii%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Here%2C%20we%20should%20avoid%20yet%20another%20attempt%20at%20analysing%20caste%20through%20class%2C%20for%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2023%2F04%2Fclass-caste-and-communism-an-interview-with-j-reghu%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJ.%20Reghu%20(Reghu%20Janardhanan)%20warned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CClass%20as%20an%20abstract%20concept%20had%20no%20bearing%20on%20Indian%20society%2C%20and%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20bearing%20even%20now.%20If%20you%20compile%20a%20list%20of%20the%2020%20richest%20men%20in%20India%20will%20there%20be%20a%20lower%20caste%20in%20it%3F%20No.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20The%20adoption%20of%20%E2%80%9Cclass%20theory%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20way%20to%20eradicate%20the%20anti-caste%20movements.%20This%20is%20of%20course%20a%20two-pronged%20strategy%2C%20which%20combines%20with%20the%20invention%20of%20Hinduism.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20from%20the%20complexity%20and%20ambiguity%20of%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20texts%20we%20should%20extricate%20another%20analytic%20instrument%20to%20read%20the%20auguries%20of%20the%20ruin.%20The%20Marxist%20term%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20lumpen%20proletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20has%20ambiguous%2C%20questionable%2C%20and%20varying%20meanings%20in%20his%20and%20Engels%E2%80%99%20writings.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20same%20can%20be%20said%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20Wallerstein%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20both%20an%20anomaly%20and%20an%20ambiguity%E2%80%9D%20concerning%20the%20meanings%20and%20origins%20of%20the%20term%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20it%20takes%20various%20functions%20in%20his%20work%20despite%20the%20%E2%80%9Canomaly%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20denotes%20a%20group%20which%20had%20come%20to%20be%20relatively%20autonomous%20in%20the%20feudal%20society%E2%80%94neither%20the%20land%20owning%20master%20nor%20the%20landless%20slave.%20However%2C%20the%20land%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20possession%20was%20insufficient%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20aristocratic%20order.%20Perhaps%2C%20this%20is%20indicated%20by%20its%20root%20in%20German%20%E2%80%9CB%C3%BCrger%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20meant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20town%20dweller%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20the%20Middle%20Ages%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eemerged%20as%20an%20intermediary%20involved%20in%20businesses%20and%20later%2C%20in%20capitalist%20societies%2C%20this%20group%20came%20to%20possess%20the%20Marxist%20sense%20of%20being%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20means%20of%20production.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eowned%20the%20time%20of%20the%20poor%20through%20the%20wage%20he%20paid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20came%20to%20further%20possess%20and%20determine%20theoretical%20and%20cultural%20production%20itself.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecame%20to%20be%20the%20group%20which%20controlled%20the%20production%20of%20goods%20and%20the%20re-production%20of%20these%20very%20systems%20of%20production%2C%20and%20held%20the%20power%20to%20assign%20meaning%20to%20all%20components%2C%20actions%2C%20and%20their%20interrelationship%20in%20society.%20It%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20terms%20to%20discuss%20Indian%20politics%20are%20determined%20by%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%3B%20that%20is%2C%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20are%20forced%20to%20lead%20their%20existence%20under%20the%20concepts%20and%20terms%20imposed%20by%20bourgeois%20Brahminism.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20total%20mastery%20of%20a%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20this%20reason%20Engels%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Marx%2C%20would%20oppose%20%E2%80%9Cmiddle%20class%20society%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20translation%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20b%C3%BCrgerliche%20Gesellschaft%E2%80%9D%20since%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marxists.org%2Farchive%2Fmarx%2Fworks%2F1852%2Fletters%2F52_09_23.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25255BManchester%25252C%25252023%252520September%2525201852%25255D%2Ci.e.%252520in%2525209%25252D10%252520days.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20class%20of%20industrial%20and%20commercial%20Capitalists%2C%20is%2C%20socially%20and%20politically%2C%20the%20ruling%20class%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20In%20Marxist%20discourse%2C%20democracies%20are%20properly%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20democracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20in%20turn%20is%20a%20scaffolding%20over%20the%20reality%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Edictatorship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20not%20the%20product%20of%20a%20historical%20rupture%20from%20an%20older%20social%20organisation%2C%20such%20as%20feudalism.%20What%20is%20today%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20homologically%20continuous%20with%20what%20was%20called%20%E2%80%9CArya%E2%80%9D%203000%20years%20ago%3A%20the%20same%20reproductively%20isolated%20group%20retained%20positions%20of%20power%20as%20the%20modes%20of%20production%20changed%20in%20history%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20feudal%2C%20industrial%20or%20techno-centric.%20And%20that%20explains%20the%20coconut%20breaking%20before%20rocket%20launches%2C%20the%20temple%20rituals%20held%20in%20technology%20firms%2C%20and%20the%20suicide%20of%20Dalits%20in%20premier%20institutions.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CAryan%20doctrine%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20superstitions%20of%20racialisation%20looms%20over%20the%20history%20of%20the%20subcontinent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findependence-on-january-22-the-noise-generated-around-it-bears-more-resemblance-to-force-a-divide%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Independence%E2%80%99%20on%20January%2022%3F%20The%20Noise%20Generated%20Is%20More%20Likely%20to%20Force%20a%20Divide%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELumpen%20in%20the%20Marxist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20proletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20comes%20from%20%E2%80%9Clumpe%E2%80%9D%20as%20used%20by%20Max%20Stirner%20to%20describe%20%E2%80%98the%20masses%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20people%20without%20regular%20employment%20or%20those%20who%20trade%20in%20the%20illicit%20or%20the%20barely%20licit%20margins%20of%20societies%E2%80%94people%20whose%20status%20ranged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.philosophy-world-democracy.org%2Farticles-1%2Ftrash-evil%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetween%20the%20refuse%20and%20the%20interior%20of%20societies%2C%20exemplified%20by%20the%20rag%20picker%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELumpen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20meant%20someone%20clothed%20in%20rags%2C%20as%20in%20the%20oft%20callously%20used%20%E2%80%9Criff-raff%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhilosophy%20had%20long%20held%20a%20certain%20suspicion%20of%20the%20people%20who%20were%20not%20bound%20to%20any%20particular%20order%20of%20regularity%2C%20as%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20Plato%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccheap%20and%20paltry%20people%E2%80%9D%20(%CF%86%CE%B1%E1%BF%A6%CE%BB%CE%BF%CF%82)%20to%20Hegel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Crabble%E2%80%9D%20and%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20proletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Platonic%20concern%20was%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20despotism%20arising%20through%20the%20instrumentalisation%20of%20the%20people%2C%20as%20seen%20later%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20Julius%20Caesar%20or%20the%20Nazis.%20Marx%20found%20something%20similar%E2%80%94a%20matter%20for%20the%20betrayal%20of%20the%20good%20end%2C%20of%20communism%E2%80%94in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20proletariat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewho%20were%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20scum%2C%20offal%2C%20refuse%20of%20all%20classes%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunist%20Manifesto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20signified%20%E2%80%9Cdanger%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20made%20evident%20in%20what%20Marx%20wrote%20of%20Napoleon%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marxists.org%2Farchive%2Fmarx%2Fworks%2F1852%2F18th-brumaire%2Fch05.htm%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Eighteenth%20Brumaire%20of%20Louis%20Bonaparte%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBonaparte%2C%20who%20precisely%20because%20he%20was%20a%20bohemian%2C%20a%20princely%20lumpen%20proletarian%2C%20had%20the%20advantage%20over%20a%20rascally%20bourgeois%20in%20that%20he%20could%20conduct%20the%20struggle%20meanly%E2%80%9D%20and%20who%20came%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echief%20of%20the%20lumpenproletariat%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarx%20failed%20to%20think%20through%20the%20political%20conditions%20of%20those%20who%20are%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpenproletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20to%20determine%20the%20precise%20concept%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdanger%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20meaning%20of%20lumpen.%20Instead%2C%20through%20an%20idiom%20of%20contempt%20and%20fear%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20addressed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpsychosis%E2%80%9D%2C%20incurable%20and%20un-addressable%20%E2%80%93%20which%20constitutes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20unconscious%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20texts.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20Rosa%20Luxembourg%20who%20produced%20a%20rigorous%20theory%20of%20lumpen%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpenproletariat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20revealed%20the%20power%20of%20this%20group.%20A%20few%20fundamental%20propositions%20on%20lumpen%20are%20to%20be%20found%20in%20her%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Russian%20Revolution%20and%20Leninism%20or%20Marxism%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(The%20University%20of%20Michigan%20Press%2C%201961%2C%20pp%2073%20%E2%80%93%2077)%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1)%20The%20lumpen%20are%20an%20essential%20component%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20embedded%E2%80%9D%20in%20bourgeois%20societies%20rather%20than%20a%20refuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2)%20The%20lumpen%20are%20a%20function%20of%20societies%20with%20hierarchical%2C%20oppressive%2C%20and%20exploitative%20self-organisation%2C%20for%20such%20social%20orders%20are%20defined%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20profoundest%20of%20immoralities%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20exploitation%20of%20man%20by%20man%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3)%20Lumpen%20is%20not%20characterised%20by%20ignorance%20nor%20by%20powerlessness%3B%20instead%2C%20it%20is%20a%20specific%20power%20to%20subvert%20the%20resources%2C%20norms%20and%20the%20laws%20of%20a%20society%20to%20produce%20profit.%20In%20the%20lumpen%20zone%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccommercial%20profiteering%2C%20fictitious%20deals%2C%20adulteration%20of%20foodstuffs%2C%20cheating%2C%20official%20embezzlement%2C%20theft%2C%20burglary%20and%20robbery%2C%20flow%20into%20one%20another%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E4)%20The%20bourgeois%2C%20from%20within%20the%20core%20of%20bourgeois%20societies%2C%20invent%20functions%20of%20profit%20using%20the%20lumpen%20to%20subvert%20and%20subordinate%20the%20norms%20and%20the%20laws%3B%20while%20remaining%20an%20entwined%20new%20force%2C%20the%20bourgeois%20is%20at%20pains%20to%20distinguish%20itself%20to%20retain%20%E2%80%9Crespectability%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20lumpen.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20group%20that%20cannot%20be%20accounted%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elogos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20within%20the%20national%20income%20accounting%20and%20refuses%20to%20accommodate%20itself%20within%20the%20regularities%20(unpredictability%20being%20its%20very%20force)%20and%20the%20legitimising%20principles%20of%20the%20modern%20state%20such%20as%20equality.%20It%20is%20analogous%20to%20what%20is%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Italy%20and%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20RSS.%20The%20lumpen%20is%20today%20the%20very%20core%20of%20what%20was%20once%20bourgeois%20societies%2C%20as%20foreseen%20by%20Luxembourg.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01134544%2FScreenshot-2024-02-01-at-1.41.56-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01134544%2FScreenshot-2024-02-01-at-1.41.56-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01134544%2FScreenshot-2024-02-01-at-1.41.56-PM-300x200.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01134544%2FScreenshot-2024-02-01-at-1.41.56-PM-1024x683.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695223%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40friendsofrss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOn%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20and%20lumpen%20Brahminism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpper%20caste%20supremacism%20(%E2%80%9CHindu%20majoritarianism%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20unity%E2%80%9D%20are%20its%20scaffolding)%20has%20two%20components%20%E2%80%93%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20and%20lumpen%20Brahminism.%20Today%2C%20nobody%20understands%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBrahminism%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20upper%20caste%20group%20Brahmin.%20Rather%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBrahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20the%20ritualistic%20consolidation%20of%20the%20hypophysical%20social%20order%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eupper%20caste%20supremacism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20had%20been%20persisting%20for%20millennia%2C%20and%20its%20theoretical%20apologetics%2C%20including%20Indian%20postcolonial%20theory.%20Brahminism%20can%20be%20served%20by%20any%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20groups%20who%20can%20exchange%20some%20of%20the%20positions%20in%20the%20social%20order%20with%20one%20another%2C%20except%20the%20right%20to%20perform%20ritualisations%20of%20purity%20which%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20caste%20group%20Brahmins%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBourgeois%20Brahminism%20is%20characterised%20by%20the%20self-presentation%20%E2%80%93%20to%20its%20own%20group%20members%2C%20to%20those%20who%20are%20lower%20in%20the%20caste%20order%2C%20and%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98west%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20of%20a%20cultural%20sophistication%20that%20bears%20semblance%20to%20the%20bourgeois%20of%20rich%20white%20nations.%20For%20the%20very%20same%20reason%2C%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20is%20competent%20to%20engage%20at%20the%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20cultural%20level%20at%20the%20international%20stage.%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBourgeois%20Brahminism%20still%20requires%20%E2%80%98respect%E2%80%99%2C%20regard%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98height%E2%80%99%20to%20exist%20in%20distinction%20from%20the%20lumpen.%20Before%20the%20arrival%20of%20modern%20law%2C%20this%20was%20possible%20because%2C%20as%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20said%2C%20the%20caste%20society%20is%20organised%20on%20%E2%80%9Can%20ascending%20scale%20of%20reverence%20and%20a%20descending%20scale%20of%20contempt%E2%80%9D%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20were%20the%20Shudras%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20p.%208).%20The%20height%20possessed%20by%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20came%20from%20esotericism%20or%20the%20inaccessibility%20of%20the%20rituals%20and%20the%20language%20in%20which%20the%20oppressive%20social%20hierarchy%20was%20encoded%20and%20founded%2C%20and%20legitimised%20its%20maintenance%20through%20force%2C%20which%20is%20a%20theme%20of%20the%20Brahminical%20epics.%20The%20repetition%20of%20the%20means%20%E2%80%93%20restriction%20of%20sexual%20relations%20to%20prevent%20miscegenation%20and%20the%20control%20of%20division%20of%20labour%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20very%20end%20ensured%20its%20survival%2C%20constituting%20a%20ceremonial%20society%20in%20the%20subcontinent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20colonial%20law%20followed%20by%20constitutional%20democracy%20arrived%20in%20what%20came%20to%20be%20the%20Indian%20republic%2C%20the%20respect%20and%20height%20enjoyed%20by%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20was%20displaced%20by%20%E2%80%9Cfear%20of%20the%20system%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20means%20of%20control%3A%20in%20order%20to%20extract%20that%20fear%2C%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20needed%20to%20be%20excluded%20from%20the%20system%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20universities%2C%20media%2C%20higher%20ranking%20military%20positions.%20When%20the%20public%20sphere%20was%20controlled%20totally%20by%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%2C%20it%20enjoyed%20the%20exchange%20of%20admiration%20and%20respect%20from%20those%20belonging%20to%20the%20same%20group%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98argumentative%20Indians%E2%80%99.%20Today%2C%20outside%20of%20the%20remnants%20of%20that%20public%20sphere%2C%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20is%20mocked%20by%20lower%20caste%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%2C%20while%20in%20the%20new%20lumpen%20public%20sphere%20serving%20the%20lumpen%20Brahminism%2C%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20is%20considered%20at%20best%20as%20an%20afterthought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20first%20emerged%20in%20colonial%20Bengal%2C%20lumpen%20Brahminism%20developed%20in%20what%20is%20today%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20defeat%20of%20a%20Brahmin%20kingdom%20by%20an%20army%20composed%20of%20lower%20caste%20soldiers%20in%201818.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20most%20influential%20and%20sophisticated%20movements%20against%20caste%20oppression%20appeared%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20led%20by%20the%20great%20Phule.%20Lumpen%20Brahminism%20developed%20against%20the%20mockery%20of%20the%20oppressive%20caste%20order%2C%20its%20myths%2C%20and%20its%20mode%20of%20life%20by%20lower%20caste%20majority%20intellectuals.%20Phule%E2%80%99s%20surgical%20precision%20could%20often%20be%20humiliating%2C%20a%20tradition%20continued%20by%20Dr.%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELumpen%20Brahminism%20never%20sought%20illusions%20of%20respectability%2C%20instead%20it%20fought%20to%20perpetuate%20the%20caste%20order%20through%20obedience%20inspired%20by%20terror.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20developing%20India%20as%20a%20lumpen%20army%20under%20perpetual%20production%20%E2%80%93%20an%20impossibility%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20will%20have%20a%20progressively%20smaller%20role.%20The%20BJP%20has%20demonstrated%20that%20its%20political%20project%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20upper%20caste%20supremacism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20masked%20and%20implemented%20through%20the%20militarisation%20of%20%E2%80%98Hinduism%E2%80%99%20will%20require%20the%20deterioration%20of%20constitutional%20and%20other%20institutions.%20This%20project%2C%20as%20it%20reaches%20closer%20towards%20its%20goals%2C%20will%20destroy%20what%20remains%20of%20the%20constitution%20itself.%20Its%20semi-literate%20leadership%2C%20as%20we%20have%20been%20witnessing%2C%20will%20damage%20relations%20with%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20and%20eventually%20imperil%20the%20Indian%20union.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20the%20left%20parties%2C%20and%20several%20of%20the%20smaller%20parties%20represented%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20in%20politics.%20Having%20%E2%80%98presentable%20faces%E2%80%99%20remains%20the%20argument%20of%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%20on%20the%20electoral%20stage%20even%20today%3B%20the%20Congress%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20today%20offer%20themselves%20as%20the%20presentable%20caretaker%20government%20of%20upper%20caste%20supremacism.%20It%20is%20these%20bourgeois%20Brahminists%20who%20allowed%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20flourish%20and%20instrumentalised%20them%20whenever%20it%20was%20suitable.%20Otherwise%2C%20why%20were%20the%20bans%20on%20the%20RSS%20ever%20lifted%3F%20Why%20were%20their%20crimes%20left%20unpunished%20in%20all%20those%20years%20when%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20held%20power%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20when%20the%20Mandal%20commission%20centred%20anti-caste%20discourses%2C%20and%20agitations%20by%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20came%20to%20assert%20their%20presence%20in%20the%20most%20unprecedented%20way%2C%20the%20upper%20castes%20understood%20that%20the%20caretaker%20function%20performed%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20various%20smaller%20parties%20would%20fail%20to%20prevent%20this%20new%20insurgency%20from%20inverting%20and%20annihilating%20the%20three%20millennia%20old%20oppressive%20social%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOf%20morals%2C%20or%20what%20is%20to%20be%20done%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20method%20in%20the%20madness%20being%20put%20on%20stage%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20unity%E2%80%9D%20narrative%20thundering%20over%20the%20public%20realm%2C%20but%20also%20of%20the%20so-called%20liberal-left%20discourses%20mocking%20the%20crude%20manners%20of%20the%20new%20custodians%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Majority%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20is%20yet%20to%20win%2050%25%20of%20votes%20polled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20They%20both%20are%20determined%20that%20India%20and%20its%20politics%20must%20be%20conceived%20and%20constructed%20on%20the%20axiom%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20majority%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20minorities%E2%80%9D.%20They%20both%20are%20resolute%20that%20the%20other%20majority%20which%20began%20to%20announce%20itself%20as%20Bahujan%20%E2%80%93%20the%20oppressed%20lower%20castes%20and%20Dalits%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20excluded%20from%20the%20axioms%20of%20what%20is%20India%2C%20its%20composition%2C%20its%20politics.%20They%20both%20portray%20anti-caste%20thought%20as%20a%20minor%20discourse%2C%20and%20a%20caste%20census%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqXohhDbkOUs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cdivisive%20agenda%E2%80%9D%20(or%20%E2%80%9Cnegative%20agenda%E2%80%9D%20for%20Ramachandra%20Guha)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20a%20misdirection%20from%20a%20developmental%20perspective%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereservations%20being%20harmful)%20for%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Several%20bourgeois%20Brahminist%20political%20commentators%20either%20supported%20the%20present%20regime%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20or%20they%20legitimise%20the%20BJP%20(and%20the%20RSS)%20even%20today%20by%20speaking%20approvingly%20of%20the%20Vajpayee%20regime%20of%201998%20%E2%80%93%202004%20which%20had%20overseen%20the%20anti-Muslim%20pogrom%20of%202002%20when%20Modi%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20a%20regime%20composed%20of%20the%20lumpen%20criminals%20behind%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20always%20been%20easier%20to%20oppose%20lumpenism%2C%20until%20it%20comes%20to%20displace%20the%20state%2C%20as%20the%20world%20found%20with%20Nazism.%20Even%20today%2C%20opposing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20terms%20made%20permissible%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20bourgeois%20Brahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94that%20is%2C%20by%20invoking%20%E2%80%9Cmajoritarianism%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cexcessive%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cshrillness%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprotection%20of%20minorities%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cilliteracy%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94is%20possible%20from%20several%20platforms%2C%20although%20these%20are%20shrinking.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20the%20unity%20of%20these%20two%20Brahminisms%20in%20upper%20caste%20supremacy%20that%20is%20difficult%20to%20address.%20This%20is%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20Brahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20criticised%20(evaluated%20according%20to%20criteria%20foreign%20to%20it)%20nor%20have%20we%20begun%20its%20critique%20(specifying%20the%20historic%20conditions%20which%20sustain%20it).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20survival%20of%20the%20republic%2C%20and%20the%20well%20being%20of%20all%20in%20the%20Indian%20Union%2C%20requires%20such%20criticism%20and%20critique.%20It%20also%20calls%20for%20a%20choice%20to%20be%20made%20by%20both%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20and%20what%20will%20remain%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebourgeois%20Brahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(as%20it%20is%20progressively%20lumpenised%2C%20and%20as%20it%20is%20progressively%20criticised)%20to%20forge%20a%20new%20struggle%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epeople%20without%20exception%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20politics%20in%20which%20there%20are%20neither%20chosen%20ones%20nor%20unseen%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elumpen%20Brahminism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20we%20should%20read%20Rosa%20Luxembourg%20again%20and%20again%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20free%20action%20of%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20rays%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20purifying%20and%20healing%20remedy%20against%20infections%20and%20disease%20germs%2C%20so%20the%20only%20healing%20and%20purifying%20sun%20is%20the%20revolution%20itself%20and%20its%20renovating%20principle%2C%20the%20spiritual%20life%2C%20activity%20and%20initiative%20of%20the%20masses%20which%20is%20called%20into%20being%20by%20it%20and%20which%20takes%20the%20form%20of%20the%20broadest%20political%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDivya%20Dwivedi%20and%20Shaj%20Mohan%20are%20philosophers%20based%20in%20the%20Subcontinent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707024648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04105808%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbourgeois-lumpen-brahminisms-republic-ayodhya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20always%20been%20easier%20to%20oppose%20lumpenis