%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20was%20then%20interrupted%20by%20the%20treasury%20benches%20when%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20got%20up%20to%20state%20that%20Gogoi%20had%20misrepresented%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20statement%20during%20her%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20president%20stated%20that%20she%20was%20addressing%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20President%20only%20addresses%20parliament%20once%20a%20year%20and%20she%20did%20so.%20Now%20whether%20she%20came%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20or%20not%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20influence%20the%20debate%20and%20his%20remarks%20should%20be%20expunged%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dubey%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20then%20said%20that%20opposition%20parliamentarians%20were%20interrupted%20during%20their%20speeches%20but%20members%20of%20the%20treasury%20benches%20could%20raise%20any%20matter%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20Union%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20when%20he%20demanded%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-demands-congress-apology-on-mps-separate-country-remark-as-opposition-walks-out-over-jharkhand%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapology%20from%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20its%20MP%2C%20D.K.%20Suresh%2C%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftax-injustice-may-compel-south-india-to-demand-a-separate-country-congress-mp-d-k-suresh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cseparate%20south%20India%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Gogoi%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Callowed%20to%20lodge%20their%20protest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20during%20the%20previous%20winter%20session%2C%20