3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%202014%2C%20slowly%20and%20steadily%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20an%20effort%20by%20the%20government%20to%20convert%20this%20temple%20of%20democracy%20into%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eraj%20darbar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bcourt%5D%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evishesh%20samrat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bspecial%20king%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirla%20then%20interrupted%20him%20again%20and%20said%20that%20he%20cannot%20make%20allegations%20against%20the%20house%20in%20which%20he%20was%20speaking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20raised%20questions%20against%20the%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Birla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20then%20said%20that%20he%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20parliamentary%20system%20in%20the%20country%20under%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20comes%20to%20the%20house%2C%20he%20is%20greeted%20with%20slogans.%20The%20responsibility%20with%20which%20we%20come%20to%20parliament%20has%20been%20forgotten.%20And%20the%20maharaja%20also%20comes%20and%20leaves%20without%20taking%20a%20single%20question%20from%20any%20department%20of%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirla%20interrupted%20him%20again%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20motion%20of%20thanks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20talking%20about%20the%20history%20of%20this%20house.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20prime%20ministers%20and%20all%20have%20abided%20by%20their%20responsibilities%20by%20answering%20questions.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20maharaja%20who%20has%20not%20answered%20a%20single%20question%20of%20any%20department%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%