%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1_11zon-1706615131-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarshit%20and%20Tanay%20Agrawal%20have%20retained%20their%20family%20legacy%20of%20mithai%20making%20with%20Pistabarfi%2C%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20Pistabarfi%20the%20new%20Janta%20Dairy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harshit.%20He%20is%20firm%20that%20the%20former%20was%20created%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20with%20a%20slightly%20different%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20end%20consumer%20is%20very%20different%20for%20both%20places.%20Janta%20Dairy%20targets%20the%20locals%20who%20have%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20shop%20since%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20time.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20repeat%20clientele.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pistabarfi%20has%20a%20niche%20audience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Pistabarfi%20delivers%20all%20over%20India%20and%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20coming%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250601%2Faarti-rastogi-bengaluru-food-startup-artinci-healthy-sugar-free-keto-friendly-gluten-free-desserts-ice-