g%20his%20thoughts%20onto%20a%20canvas.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20forested%20surroundings%2C%20he%20would%20often%20paint%20bamboo%20on%20most%20of%20his%20acrylic%20and%20oil%20paintings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudying%20deeper%2C%20he%20understood%20how%20numerous%20bamboo%20tribes%20differ%20from%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20while%20some%20species%20have%20large%20and%20straight%20culms%2C%20some%20are%20smaller%20and%20more%20flexible.%20Some%20have%20thick%20walls%20and%20stiff%20hair%20on%20the%20nodes%2C%20while%20some%20boast%20different%20leaf%20textures%20that%20might%20go%20unnoticed%20to%20the%20untrained%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%20all%20bamboos%20have%20different%20leaves%2C%20shoots%2C%20and%20structures.%20I%20was%20so%20fascinated%20by%20them%20that%20I%20decided%20to%20collect%20them%20one%20by%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2053-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20paintings%2C%20Johnson%20travelled%20far%20and%20wide%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195033%2Farunachal-pradesh-tourism-must-visit-culture-books-bamboo-cups%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econserve%20bamboo%20%3C%2Fa%3Evarieties.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20a%20proud%20owner%20of%20the%2017-acre%20plantation%20that%20boasts%2010%2C000%20plants%20including%20a%20rare%20collection%20of%20142%20species%20collected%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnson%20travelled%20far%20and%20wide%20to%20conserve%20bamboo%20varieties%20beyond%20his%20paintings.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2