0life%2C%20and%20six%20months%20is%20just%20a%20small%20part%20of%20your%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20her%20leadership%2C%20Edelweiss%20Asset%20Management%20Limited%20currently%20manages%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore.%20She%20is%20looking%20to%20invest%20in%20young%20companies%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20part%20of%20the%20show%2C%20she%20says%20she%20feels%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335548%2Fthis-hero-turned-mud-walls-into-blackboards-streets-into-schools-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeels%20optimistic%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20India%2C%20seeing%20the%20limitless%20potential%20of%20the%20young%20entrepreneurs%20on%20the%20show.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20takeaway%20from%20the%20show%20for%20me%20has%20been%20the%20fact%20that%20young%20Indians%20are%20truly%20limitless.%20And%20they%20are%20from%20Tier%203%20and%204%20towns%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20doing%20so%20much%20with%20limited%20resources%20and%20under%20difficult%20circumstances.%20I%E2%80%99m%20buoyed%20about%20finding%20young%20talent%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20everyone%20young%20or%20old%2C%20Radhika%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFind%20your%20sky%20and%20learn%20to%20fly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20conspires%20to%20make%20you%20succeed%20if%20you%20want%20it%20hard%20enough.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20connect%20the%20dots%20but%20the%20dots%20start%20connecting.%20Each%20one%20of%20us%20is%20unique%20and%20different.%20Celebrate%20your%20perfections%20and%20imperfections%20and%20everything%20in%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20story%2C%20too%2C%20can%20have%20a%20happy%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706076791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FGV